source: Drive the backbone of Britain! Experience the power and pace of modern electric traction along the West Coast Main Line between Birmingham and Crewe. Weave through a mix of busy city stations, rural landscapes, and historic junctions as you tackle steep gradients, high-speed running, and frequent stopping patterns. From the heart of the Midlands to the gateway of the North West, this classic main line is yours to master in Train Sim World.
Translation: 驾驶英国的脊梁铁路！体验伯明翰和克鲁之间西海岸干线上现代电力机车的澎湃动力和速度。穿梭于繁忙的城市车站、乡村风光和历史悠久的交汇处，挑战陡峭的坡度、高速行驶和频繁的停靠。从英格兰中部中心地带到西北门户，这条经典干线在《模拟火车世界》中等你来征服。
